data.description: Welcome to Birdsong Cottage! Prepare to be AMAZED! This spectacular multi-generational home will suit your many needs! The main level ranch features 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, hardwood flooring, updated appliances, fireplace and a fabulous rear screened porch and patio! The terrace level is completely finished with two bedrooms, den, kitchen and a separate covered porch and even a separate driveway! Plenty of space and privacy for TWO families to live comfortably - each with their own address! DonCOt miss this one!!
